CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 17, 1962, pg. 17 reads: "Double Birthday - Tiny tots Kim Miller and her brother, Lloyd, celebrated their fourth and third birthdays, respectively, together with their family and friends. Shown with the two are, left to right: Jason Scott, Ronald Scott, James Dorsey Jr., Joseph Miller and Blanche Miller. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Jason Scott, Ronald Scott, James Dorsey Jr., Joseph Miller, and Blanche Miller, gathered around Kim and Lloyd Miller, for birthday party in domestic interior with striped curtains and carved dining chairs, another pose
